                  , did, by virtue of such employment, take into his possession the sum of 5s. of and from one 
                     <persName id="t18010114-60-person646">
                        Joseph 
                        Fallows
                     <interp inst="t18010114-60-person646" type="surname" value="Fallows"></interp>
